    Natalie Grima
Maintainer: Leon Kinsella <Leon.Kinsella@hdr.mq.edu.au>
Description: Makes it easier to create graphics used in genomics. Graphics included are:
    PCA,
    Volcano Plots,
    Summary tables,
    Karyoplots, and
    Venn Diagramms.
